dehintergründen und einer dispositionellen Grundstruktur erklärt wird. Die überraschende Lösung ist das Ergebnis einer eingehenden Analyse von Dispositions- und Fähigkeitsausdrücken.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aGerman languagexModality. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  Sprachwissenschaft 2005-2012z9783110346824oZDB-23-OSQ0 cprintz978305004909040uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978305006234140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783050062341423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783050062341/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DLSc2000d2014  aZDB-23-OSQc2005d2012